title: Ponzu-Glazed Chicken Sandos with Cucumber & Spicy Mayo
description: Check out this delicious, easy-to-make meal designed by our chefs to help you meet your goals in time for warm weather fun. In just 10 minutes, you’ll be digging into succulent, flavorful ponzu-glazed chicken on a fluffy brioche bun with crunchy cukes and a spicy gochujang mayo. With this light, quick lunch, you’ll have more time to get outside and play!
